#photienthanh my friend talked so much about this #pho place, I was at the time super exhausted from the out of town meeting, but the glow appeared on her face when mentioning Pho Tien Thanh convinced me a trip to this seemingly sketchy pho joint. So soup base is the best I've ever had in Toronto. But the off menu order of #pigfeet and #pigblood made my day. For those who aren't able to enjoy such Asian delicacy, I feel bad for them. 4.5/5. Loving the #vietnamese street style decor and the crazy greens that acts as curtains as well. The pig feet is $2.5 and pig blood is $5 a small bowl.
